# React + shadcn/ui

- Use functional React components with named exports.
- Generated shadcn primitives live in `src/components/ui/**`; update with shadcn tooling.
- Keep layouts mobile-first, accessible, keyboard navigable, and WCAG 2.1 AA oriented.
- Use Lucide icons via named imports when icons are needed.
- Keep UI text in i18n resource files unless it is test-only copy.
